{"type": "article", "id": 21795, "title": "Z Modular System & I Series & Q2 Ottoman by ODESD2", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-03T08:14:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150126mT8LFX3pUxfEt4wJ.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">乌克兰的设计公司 ODESD2 新推出了这些家具，大都用了很酷的黑色和几何图形。黑色的架子是由一种立方体组成，6 个面中只有一个面完全遮盖，其余被斜切着半遮盖或者只留一个空架子。依照不同方向堆起来形成了特别的装饰和几何效果。沙发类似于军用垫，很方正，根据扣带来改变形状。另有一个躺椅是由无数三角形组成的，支撑处也是尖锐的三角锥，让人觉得特立独行。点击<a href=\"http://odesd2.com/en/furniture/modular-systems/z_set_1\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150124BDxfCnUh7eEdSTPu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.72666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150124yEshq25owIe6k4xG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061501255KQFyrlhsWOwiY6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.785\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150125Sj9YCkFoleZpAsm1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150125iRIS3ckmxUbpugvn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150126czobtAvkWEiHDNXU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}